-Qualitaet. Via UnetLoaderGGUF.\n\nFILES:\n- diffusion_models: 2x WAN (high + low noise)\n- text_encoders: UMT5 (CLIPLoader type 'wan')\n- vae: WAN/wan2.2_vae\n\nREGELN:\n- Frames = 4n+1 (81 = ~5s @16fps)\n- Zwei-Experten-Sampling: high noise zuerst, dann low noise\n- Mit lightx2v 4-Step-LoRAs: 4 Steps total (2 high + 2 low), CFG=1\n- Ohne LoRAs: 20-30 Steps, CFG 3.5-5\n\nNegativ-Prompt ist der chinesische WAN-Standard (laesst Artefakte weg)."],"color":"#653","bgcolor":"#432"},{"id":17,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[40,760],"size":[380,300],"flags":{},"order":6,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"title":"📥 Modelle & Downloads","properties":{"Node name for S&R":"MarkdownNote","cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.68"},"widgets_values":["**WAN 2.2 I2V 14B GGUF Q8 lightx2v**\n\n- unet (GGUF): `WAN/wan2.2_i2v_A14b_high_noise_lightx2v_4step_720p_260412-Q8_0.gguf` + low\n- text_encoders: `UMT5/umt5_xxl_fp8_e4m3fn_scaled.safetensors`\n- vae: `WAN/wan2.2_vae.safetensors`\n\n**4 Steps, lightx2v eingebacken — keine LoRA noetig. Braucht ComfyUI-GGUF.**"],"color":"#222","bgcolor":"#111"}],"links":[[1,1,0,2,0,"MODEL"],[2,3,0,4,0,"MODEL"],[3,5,0,6,0,"CLIP"],[4,5,0,7,0,"CLIP"],[5,9,0,10,0,"VAE"],[6,8,0,10,1,"IMAGE"],[7,2,0,11,0,"MODEL"],[8,6,0,11,1,"CONDITIONING"],[9,7,0,11,2,"CONDITIONING"],[10,10,0,11,3,"LATENT"],[11,4,0,12,0,"MODEL"],[12,6,0,12,1,"CONDITIONING"],[13,7,0,12,2,"CONDITIONING"],[14,11,0,12,3,"LATENT"],[15,12,0,13,0,"LATENT"],[16,9,0,13,1,"VAE"],[17,13,0,14,0,"IMAGE"],[18,14,0,15,0,"VIDEO"]],"groups":[],"config":{},"extra":{"ds":{"scale":0.7,"offset":[0,0]}},"version":0.4}